    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and cook for 3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1580808075441-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
