            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, stack your <strong>tortillas</strong> and slice into triangles</p><p>Add the <strong>tortilla triangles</strong> to a tray (or two!) with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Toss everything together then spread them out and put the tray[s] in the oven for 5-7 min or until lightly browned and crisp – these are your <strong>nachos</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1580808079724-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
