          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1580808079724-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince has browned, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground cumin</strong> and <strong>remaining ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min or until all the mince is coated in the spices</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>kidney beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1580808083881-x200.jpg",
