            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is thickening, trim, then roughly chop your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Roughly dice your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong>, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
