          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong>,<strong> tomato</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your<strong> tomato salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
